    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the single-load-level validation is consistent with ASTM F1717 normative requirements and is acceptable for the current submission scope. Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory decision-making.",
